  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à qtermwidget</title>

    <para>
      As the name suggests, the <application>qtermwidget</application> is a
      terminal widget for <application>Qt</application>.
    </para>

    &lfs77_checked; &gcc5_checked;

